::Shadow Wing/ Spears::

Shadow Wing::
She took a hit in the wing and let out a screech.  She flew to a tall 
tree and perched.  She could fly, but barely.  She knew she was out 
of this one for a bit. She sat on the branch watching the fluid run 
out of her wing.  She yelled at the Anubis, "JERK!"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Spears:: 
She was hit and the blast knocked her around. In that spiked ballm 
she was able to take more damage than in her bot form.  But that last 
blast hurt a lot.  She rolled to behind a rock.  She transformed into 
bot mode and checked the damage. A lot of her quills were damaged, 
she had cuts and small gashes on her legs and arms.  Her chest and 
torso was relatively OK.  She pulled out a quill. She threw it at 
Hades, aiming for his chest.
